    "Nevertheless, it has to be considered, that the feed conversion efficiency of BSF is temperature-dependent (Chia et al., 2018).",
    "It may be inferred that temperature-controlled raising containers are required for insects to gain maximum mass in the shortest amount of time, use the least amount of food, and emit the fewest amount of emissions, which indicates greater energy consumption than for conventional livestock (Rumpold & Schlüter, 2013).",
